#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.27:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Koṭigāmavagga"
msgstr "3. At the Village of Koṭi"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Tathasutta"
msgstr "27. Real"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.27:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ariyasaccāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four noble truths."

msgctxt "sn56.27:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn56.27:1.3"
msgid ""
"Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ "
"ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.27:1.4"
msgid ""
"imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ariyasaccāni tathāni avitathāni anaññathāni;"
msgstr "These four things are real, not unreal, not otherwise."

msgctxt "sn56.27:1.5"
msgid "tasmā ‘ariyasaccānī’ti vuccanti."
msgstr "That’s why they’re called ‘noble truths’."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.27:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.27:2.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
